# Managed by rosary (rosary-05fbe0). The bead-store BINARY is local — never
# git-tracked: a binary DB has no git 3-way merge, so ordinary resolutions
# (checkout --theirs/--ours, reset --hard, stash pop) silently eat live bead
# state. Bead CONTENT is shared via the tracked, mergeable .beads/beads.jsonl.

# SQLite store + sidecars (local only)
beads.db
beads.db-shm
beads.db-wal
beads.db-journal
beads.db.migrated
*.db
*.db-shm
*.db-wal
*.db-journal

# Dolt store + server runtime
dolt/
dolt-server.pid
dolt-server.log
dolt-server.port
dolt-server.lock
dolt-access.lock

# Host-local runtime
.beads-credential-key
.local_version
last-touched
backup/
